data.description: Located centrally in Sulphur, this home is on a cul de sac and features a lower-level master suite and huge bonus game-room.  Upstairs are 4 additional bedrooms and a full bath.  Large lot!  Backyard hosts a small mother in law space.  With some TLC, this home could be restored to her former beauty.  Seller willing to also negotiate furnishings. Buyers please note:  Flood zone is AE, and premium with USAA is $3,729 annually.  All measurements are  more or less. Home to be sold as-is, no repairs.
